---
import SimpleLayout from '../layouts/SimpleLayout.astro';
---

<SimpleLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How thewideangle.club collects and uses data." eyebrow="Legal">
  <p><em>Last updated: 19 July 2026.</em></p>
  <p>
    This policy explains what data thewideangle.club (&ldquo;we&rdquo;, &ldquo;the site&rdquo;) collects when you visit,
    and how it is used. We aim to collect the minimum necessary to run and improve the publication.
  </p>
  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics 4 and Umami (cookieless) record pageviews, referral source, device
      type, and on-site events (scroll depth, affiliate clicks, search queries).</li>
    <li><strong>Get in Touch form:</strong> if you message us via the form on this site, your name, email, phone
      (if provided), and message are sent to us through EmailJS so we can respond. We don't add you to any
      mailing list from this.</li>
    <li><strong>WhatsApp / Instagram / Email:</strong> if you reach us directly on WhatsApp, Instagram, or email,
      that conversation is governed by that platform's own privacy policy as well as this one.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    Google Analytics may set cookies for measurement. Umami is cookieless by design. Where required, a
    consent banner is shown before non-essential cookies are set, in line with India&rsquo;s DPDP Act and
    GDPR where applicable.
  </p>
  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>
    We may display ads via Google AdSense once approved. AdSense may use cookies/identifiers to serve
    relevant ads; see Google&rsquo;s own privacy policy for how it processes that data.
  </p>
  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by
    <a href="/contact/">contacting us</a>.
  </p>
  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy as the site evolves; the &ldquo;last updated&rdquo; date above will always reflect the latest version.</p>
</SimpleLayout>
